1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Ren still couldn't understand the message.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Kyrie closed the black page and said the missing student was the price of his awakening.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,000
The black ink on Ren's hand began to glow.

4
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:11,000
She told him he had been chosen long before the monster found him.

